## gpio-controller

**Value type:** `<empty>`

The presence of a *gpio-controller* property marks the node as a GPIO controller. No value is required — the presence of the property is sufficient.

```dts
/* arch/arm64/boot/dts/allwinner/sun50i-h6.dtsi */
pio: pinctrl@300b000 {
    compatible = "allwinner,sun50i-h6-pinctrl";
    gpio-controller;
    #gpio-cells = <3>;
};
```
